==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Apparently from [[ἄγριος]] {{GG|66}} and [[ἵππος]] {{GG|2462}}; wild-horse tamer; 

===Pronunciation===
*Ἀγρίππας / Agrippas / ag-rip'-pas

===Proper noun===
'''Ἀγρίππας'''

# [[Agrippas]], one of the Herods: - [[Agrippa]].

